column2: SELECT TOP # PhotoObjAll.objid, zooVotes.nvote_tot, zooVotes.p_el, zooVotes.p_cw, zooVotes.p_acw, zooVotes.p_edge, zooVotes.p_dk, zooVotes.p_mg, zooVotes.p_cs into MyTable from PhotoObjAll join zooVotes on PhotoObjAll.objid = zooVotes.objid SELECT TOP # t1.nvote_tot, count (t1.p_el) as cnt, (SELECT count (t2.p_el) FROM zooVotes t2 WHERE t2.nvote_tot > = t1.nvote_tot) into MyTable_cnt2 from zooVotes t1 group by t1.nvote_tot order by t1.nvote_tot desc
